title: Day 6 post op FFS Dr. Ramenini
author: LyssaPaige917
selftext: Not the best picture still very swollen. Excited to see what my nose looks like. Was finally able to wash my hair yesterday. Can definitely see changes. My hairline incision is precise.  Not in any pain. I had hairline advancement, brow bone shave and orbital bone, rhinoplasty, fat transfer into my cheeks and chin and silicone removed from my chin.
